Which obviously begs the question: do we ever want to convert back.
Given your hint for converting [GetWalletForJSONRPCRequest](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/34844#issuecomment-4267662343) it may be necessary (unless we propagate the type further), but I agree with you that this could also be done in a followup.

